race.description: Ridgeport 2026 Mm Yearlings Epona Classic Hcp
race.comment: SUPERNATURAL (2) is first-up here and has won twice when fresh in the past. His recent trial was very solid and he looks set to run well fresh. Likely to get back in the run, but Pike knows him well and if he can be close to his best on resumption, he'll be hard to hold out. JAZ SESSION (1) won in this grade two back before getting too far out of her ground last time out when a $4.40 chance in a 72+. Might need some luck from the inside draw, but back to this grade is a big tick and a return to her best form is on the cards. TRIPLE THE CHANT (4) is likely to be better over further but her recent trial was solid and she has placed first-up in the past. Form from behind her last campaign stood up and she can go to another level this time in work. LUCKY I AM (3) just missed fresh when gunned down late. Fitter now and can make every post a winner. DEFINE BEAUTIFUL (7) comes here on the fresh side in what looks a targeted attack. Can't be left out.
